"{\"uid\": \"newzimbabwe.com-zimbabwe-chess-sends-team-to-2024-olympiad\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Date:  By Sports Reporter  ZIMBABWE Chess Federation (ZCF) is hoping for a positive outing after sending a team of 11 players to the 45th FIDE Chess Olympiad, which kicks off Tuesday in Budapest, Hungary.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 35, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 0.9999999651927288, \"rank\": 3.473957507078414e-08, \"text\": \"ZIMBABWE\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}, {\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 41, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chess\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 2.8865934487090785e-12, \"text\": \"Chess\", \"types\": [\"Q1914636\", \"Q11410\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chess\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chess\"}, {\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999993142148547, \"rank\": 6.654207831367473e-07, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.7864800468273991, \"rank\": 0.270771324700169, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prestigious international tournament will run for 13 days with more than 50 countries participating.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zimbabwe's team was sent off Monday afternoon thanks to Minerva Risk Advisors, who came through with sponsorship.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 0.9999999651927288, \"rank\": 3.473957507078414e-08, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}, {\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minerva\", \"score\": 0.9999645113906823, \"rank\": 2.1321480686756927e-05, \"text\": \"Minerva\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minerva\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minerva\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking during the send off, ZCF secretary general, Todd Mapingire expressed confidence in the team which he said will return victorious.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Grimshaw\", \"score\": 0.9843404357104051, \"rank\": 0.015905317912815808, \"text\": \"Todd\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Grimshaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Grimshaw\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have charged up that we are going to come back home with something, that is our hope.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If something else comes up its not our hope because we believe we can do well with this team we are sending,\\\" said Mapingire.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zimbabwe is being led by veteran player Tapiwa Gora as team captain and he is one of the medal hopefuls.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 0.9999999651927288, \"rank\": 3.473957507078414e-08, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}, {\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gopa